A very simple XMPP bot for todo list.

Original idea belongs to Dendiz, see [1] for his project.
Since his project requires Java, I created Python version. 

Wokkel idea comes from metajack.[2]

[1] http://dendiz.com/blog/?page_id=188/
[2] http://metajack.im/2008/09/25/an-xmpp-echo-bot-with-twisted-and-wokkel/

Requirements:
 * Python
 * Python-twisted > 8.x
 * Wokkel



For Wokkel:
1. Checkout Wokkel code from here:
https://svn.ik.nu/wokkel/trunk/
2. Install:
python setup.py install
